      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.25rem);font-weight:400;color:#f0ece4;line-height:1.12;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        What Is a Contract of Sale in Queensland? A Seller's Guide
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        The REIQ contract is the legal foundation of every Queensland property transaction. Understanding what it covers and what happens between signing and settlement gives you confidence at every step.
      </p>
